description: Clean Motion AB engages in the development, production, and sale of vehicle solutions to the transportation sector. The company is headquartered in Lerum, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2016-05-26. The firm develops an electrical vehicle Zbee that is an energy efficient vehicle for short distance transportation of up to three people and smaller goods. The firm's product creates no noise or local pollution, and it works towards reducing global carbon emissions. The company is made from fibre reinforced plastic (FRP) material that ensures lightweight and safety features.
naics: Semiconductor and Other Electronic Component Manufacturing
name: Clean Motion AB
